 can hinder your effectiveness. It takes a strong manager to keep all of them in perspective. It is natural to violate them when detractors enter the picture or when encountering challenges in a role.', 'Becoming an Effective Manager', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '108-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-01 18:27:53', '2016-07-01 15:27:53', '', 108, 'http://www.buluma.me.ke/108-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
